You don't see them around much.

300
00:27:40.289 --> 00:27:41.754
Yeah.

301
00:27:41.856 --> 00:27:43.320
They're my dad's
cameras actually.

302
00:27:45.297 --> 00:27:47.128
No worries. not dead.

303
00:27:47.230 --> 00:27:48.496
He's...

304
