you're really angry about it.

309
00:28:16.157 --> 00:28:18.659
and I know you think
I don't know shit. but...

310
00:28:18.761 --> 00:28:21.091
I'm not angry about that. Jesse.

311
00:28:21.193 --> 00:28:23.796
