499
00:49:46.042 --> 00:49:47.315
Okay.

500
00:49:47.417 --> 00:49:48.512
One more.

501
00:49:54.855 --> 00:49:56.351
- Lee.
- Yes.

502
00:49:56.453 --> 00:49:58.527
