516
00:50:58.147 --> 00:51:00.054
So weird.

517
00:51:00.156 --> 00:51:02.520
This place is like
everything I'd forgotten.

518
00:51:03.394 --> 00:51:04.523
Funny.

519
00:51:04.625 --> 00:51:07.426
I was thinking it felt like
